w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Billie-Eillish-Performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Billie-Eillish-Performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Billie-Eillish-Performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Billie-Eillish-Performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>分享了她的观点，认为<a href="/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a>的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-lana-del-rey-12692-320858">Born To Die</a> 》“改变了音乐”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lana-del-rey-live-in-london-review-setlist-photos-hyde-park-3466933">拉娜·德尔·雷 (Lana Del Rey) 伦敦现场演出：真正伟大人物的职业生涯定义时刻</a></strong></li></ul><p>Eilish 出现在 Dua Lipa 的<em>At Your Service</em>播客的最新一集中，被问及她成长过程中听过的专辑以及这些专辑对她过去和现在的意义。</p><p> “我女儿拉娜的《生而死》，”她回答道。 “我觉得这张专辑改变了音乐，尤其是改变了女孩的音乐以及可能性的潜力。我想说， <a href="/artists/childish-gambino">Childish Gambino</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-calls-because-the-internet-the-rap-ok-computer-3201133">因为互联网</a>》是另一首真正改变了我看待音乐和专辑的方式的歌曲。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：Billie Eilish：成长之路" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/1Mc30pmvv8Qaw3d50xjd5f?go=1&#038;sp_cid=72d8e289f4f4e5aaf9d8468db9286e1a&#038;utm_source=oembed&#038;utm_medium=desktop&#038;nd=1"></iframe></p><p>她补充道：“<a href="/artists/justin-bieber">贾斯汀·比伯</a>的《相信》，宝贝。那是我的狗屎。我不能……还有“日记”，贾斯汀·比伯，“日记”。这些都是一些很棒的专辑，非常非常好。说实话，被<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-neighbourhood">邻居</a>‘消灭<em>’</em>了。”</p><p>艾利什后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-the-creative-process-is-different-with-her-next-album-3485296">公开了她在制作第三张专辑时创作过程中发生的变化</a>。</p><p>这位格莱美奖获奖歌手说：“一切都不同了。我最近一直在尝试比较它，只是因为我习惯了以不同的方式来做。并试图表现得像，‘这样做没关系。我可以。我仍然能够做到这一点；我还有能力。”</p><p>她还反思了她与哥哥兼制作人<a href="/artists/finneas">Finneas</a>的关系，并分享了两人在制作第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-happier-than-ever-review-3006594">《Happier Than Ever》</a>时如何产生了良好的化学反应。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwFZkXps2Dz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.6