2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games">Epic Games</a>宣布了新的<a href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/news/introducing-the-epic-first-run-program" target="_blank" rel="noopener">首次运行</a>计划，该计划为参与者提供 100% 的净收入，为期六个月的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games-store">Epic Games Store</a>独占权。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-aaa-games-industry-is-doomed-3391969">AAA 游戏产业注定要失败</a></strong></li></ul><p>对于注册了 Epic Games 开发者帐户并正在开发 10 月 16 日或之后推出的合格产品的开发者和发行商来说，他们将受益于用户支出带来的净收入增加以及对潜在客户的“持续曝光”。</p><p> Epic Games Store 每月有 6800 万活跃用户，那些注册 Epic First Run 计划的人将看到他们的游戏获得“新的独家徽章、主页展示位置和专用收藏”。</p><p>此外，他们的产品将“在相关商店活动中亮相，包括销售、活动和社论（如适用）”。另一方面，该公司强调开发商“必须尽早并经常向目标受众推广他们的产品”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3488027" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3488027" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3488027" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/epic-games-store-exclusivity-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488027" class="wp-caption-text">一个人在电脑上玩游戏 图片来源：Fredrick Tendong 来自 Unsplash</figcaption></figure><p> Epic First Run 还允许开发者在其发行商的商店或启动器上发布他们的产品，直接销售给客户。此外，如果开发商通过竞争对手发布游戏，则独占期从当天起失效，收入分成恢复到标准。</p><p>一旦这六个月结束，开发者就可以将他们的产品放到其他第三方平台上，收入分成将缩减至 88%。</p><p>该公司表示：“将您的游戏带到 Epic Games Store 从未如此简单。” “今年 3 月，我们推出了自助发布工具，以简化入门和发布流程。这些工具允许开发者直接通过 Epic 开发者门户注册、设置、测试和分发他们的游戏。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，菲尔·斯宾塞表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-absence-on-xbox-is-an-issue-says-phil-spencer-3487897">Xbox 发布的功能对等政策导致了</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-absence-on-xbox-is-an-issue-says-phil-spencer-3487897">《博德之门 3》</a></em>等游戏的延迟，但这仍然是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-absence-on-xbox-is-an-issue-says-phil-spencer-3487897">微软</a>的优先事项。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/epic-games-is-giving-developers-100-per-cent-of-revenue-for-total-exclusivity-3488016">Epic Games 给予开发商 100% 收入以获得完全独占权的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 OMD 宣布新专辑并分享单曲《Bauhaus Staircase》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/omd-announce-new-album-and-share-single-bauhaus-staircase-listen-preorder-3488022?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=omd-announce-new-专辑和分享单包豪斯楼梯收听预购Liberty DunworthThu, 24 Aug 2023 10:57:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3488022 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023年OMD" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张专辑将是他们自 2017 年以来的第一张新 LP</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/omd-announce-new-album-and-share-single-bauhaus-staircase-listen-preorder-3488022">OMD 宣布新专辑并分享单曲“Bauhaus Staircase”后</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2023年OMD" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/omd">OMD</a>宣布回归，并推出了新专辑《Bauhaus Staircase》，这是他们六年来的首张新唱片。看看下面的标题曲目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-andy-mccluskey-orchestral-manoeuvres-in-the-dark-omd-2556689">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ – 安迪·麦克拉斯基 (Andy McCluskey)，《黑暗中的管弦乐演习》(OMD)</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>即将发行的专辑是乐队自去年庆祝成立 40 周年以来首次发布的公告，也是自 2017 年推出广受好评的第 13 张录音室专辑《The Punishment of Luxury》以来的首张新音乐。</p><p>即将发行的唱片主要由麦克拉斯基和保罗·汉弗莱斯这两位成员创作、录制和混音，预计将成为 Orchestral Maneuvers in the Dark 迄今为止最明确的政治唱片。它还体现了他们“既成为斯托克豪森又成为阿巴”的愿望，是在 COVID-19 封锁期间写成的。</p><p> “我重新发现了完全无聊的创造力，”麦克拉斯基承认这个项目，暗示了实验声音背后的根源和其背后的政治动机。</p><p>两人还与摇滚制作人大卫·沃茨 (David Watts) 合作，为谢菲尔德乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-reytons">The Reytons</a>最近的排行榜冠军专辑执导，他将两首歌曲混音。 </p><figure id="attachment_3488024" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3488024" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3488024" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000.jpg" alt="OMD &#39;Bauhaus Staircase&#39; 专辑封面" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/OMD-album-artwork@2000x2000-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3488024" class="wp-caption-text"> OMD &#39;Bauhaus Staircase&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>“我对我们在这张唱片上所做的一切感到非常满意，”麦克拉斯基解释说，回顾了乐队在利物浦首次演出以来的 45 年。 “如果这是 OMD 的最后声明，我会很放心。”</p><p> 《Bauhaus Staircase》将于 10 月 27 日通过 White Noise 发售。 <a href="https://omd.uk.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> to pre-order the album.</p><p> In celebration of the announcement of the new album, the members have also shared their first single to be taken from the LP. The title track, which is also the song that opens the album, serves as a nod to McCluskey&#39;s love of the Bauhaus era.</p><p> It also looks to reflect on the power of protest art and works as “a metaphor” for how artistic passion can demonstrate strength in the face of criticism and adversity.</p><p> “When times are hard there is a tendency for Governments to look at cutting funding for creativity, just at the moment when the arts are most needed to nourish our souls. Thus, it seems appropriate that the song and its eponymous album were created during Covid Lockdown,” said McCluskey of the song.</p><p> “Sonically, the track attacks you instantly with rasping analogue synths, soaring electronic melodies, and pounding 808 drums. And the energy just keeps ramping up for four minutes.” Check out the track below. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Orchestral Manoeuvres in the Dark - Bauhaus Staircase (Official Video)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/EFpIz0RQU9c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Later this year, OMD will take to the stage at this year&#39;s edition of the Darker Waves Festival. Held in Huntington, California on November 18, the event will see the band perform alongside acts including <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/new-order">New Order</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tears-for-fears">Tears for Fears</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-cell">Soft Cell</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/devo">DEVO</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/echo-and-the-bunnymen">Echo &amp; The Bunnymen</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-psychedelic-furs">The Psychedelic Furs</a> , and more.</p><p> In other OMD news, back in 2019, McCluskey took part in <em>NME</em> ’s <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-andy-mccluskey-orchestral-manoeuvres-in-the-dark-omd-2556689" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Does Rock N&#39; Roll Kill Braincells?!</em></a> Series, and reflected on the band&#39;s track &#39;Enola Gay&#39; being banned by BBC children&#39;s TV show <em>Swap Shop.</em></p><p> “I don&#39;t know how they conjured that up as we&#39;d done loads of press about the fact it was about the aeroplane that dropped the atom bomb,” he said. “Bizarre! (Adopts an archetypal old-fashioned BBC suit voice) &#39;It&#39;ll be fine if it&#39;s questioning the morality of dropping atom bombs but we don&#39;t want the word &#39;gay&#39; on kids&#39; morning TV!&#39;. We were gobsmacked they could get such the wrong end of the stick.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/omd-announce-new-album-and-share-single-bauhaus-staircase-listen-preorder-3488022">OMD announce new album and share single &#39;Bauhaus Staircase&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
